41Result
42Reader::decode(const BinaryBitmap& image) const
43{
44 auto binImg = image.getBlackMatrix();
45 if (binImg == nullptr) {
46 return Result(DecodeStatus::NotFound);
47 }
48
49 auto detectorResult = Detector::Detect(*binImg, _tryHarder, _isPure);
50 if (!detectorResult.isValid())
51 return Result(DecodeStatus::NotFound);
52
53 auto decoderResult = Decoder::Decode(detectorResult.bits(), _charset);
54 auto position = detectorResult.position();
55
56 // If the code was mirrored: swap the bottom-left and the top-right position.
57 // No need to 'fix' top-left and alignment pattern.
58 if (decoderResult.extra() && static_cast<DecoderMetadata*>(decoderResult.extra().get())->isMirrored()) {
59 std::swap(position[1], position[3]);
60 }
61
62 return Result(std::move(decoderResult), std::move(position), BarcodeFormat::QR_CODE);
63}
